### Base Config
Compression yes
ForwardX11 yes

TCPKeepAlive no
ServerAliveCountMax 3
ServerAliveInterval 150

## Use identity file as default
IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa

## Set loglevel details
LogLevel QUIET

## Enable X11 Forward
ForwardX11 yes

## Sharing connecitons
ControlMaster auto
ControlPath  ~/.ssh/sockets/%r@%h-%p
ControlPersist 600

## Include directives
Include private.d/*
Include work.d/*
# Include archive.d/*